title: Fetish: The Dream Scape
overview: FETISH, THE DREAM SCAPE, from acclaimed photographer Laurent Sky, making his directorial debut and bringing his highly-stylized photographer`s vision to video with the first in this striking new series. Five scorching surreal scenes, a technicolor landscape plummeting through the sexual nightmares of Laurent Sky. Industrial hardcore sex never seen before awaits in this one-of-a-kind series.
